Key for identification of this group of species of the Podalydioides group of 
<taxonomicName id="0ECA4D45FFAD5310BAB1CD24103AF9B0" authority="Kunth" box="[994,1139,1628,1653]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Brongniartia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
